timeline
    title Comeketo Agent — Project Decisions Timeline

    section 2026-04-28 (Phase 1-5 ledger buildout era — foundational decisions)
        DEC-001 GitHub Source of Truth : durable versioned memory beats local + chat
        DEC-002 FileTree Over RAG : explicit file-tree continuity beats opaque retrieval
        DEC-003 Client Boxes Canonical : Auto/Client Boxes/&lt;Name&gt;/ owns client truth
        DEC-004 Plans Are Strategy Drafts : seven-day plans never auto-authorize sends
        DEC-005 Risky Moves Need Isolated Approval : fee waivers/discounts/scope require explicit approval
        DEC-006 Boxes Page Is Display Only : UI shows truth, never owns it
        DEC-007 Sitemap Is UI Done Gate : page changes update sitemap in same unit of work
        DEC-008 One Ledger At A Time : ledgers built sequentially with user P signal

    section 2026-04-29 (architectural settling — post-Phase-5)
        DEC-2026-04-29-001 Triad Spine : Box + Ledger + Sub-agent for everything stateful
        DEC-2026-04-29-002 Three-Phase Build : A=Ledgers (current) → B=Sub-agents → C=Subagent Boxes
        DEC-2026-04-29-003 TCL/GL Update Discipline : orientation surfaces update in same unit of work as the change
        DEC-2026-04-29-004 Audit Ledger Out-of-Scope : coverage absorbed by Open Problems / Decisions / Communications / per-Box
